question.string: has life expectancy in iran grown in any year after 1999?

query.sparql:
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>
    PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
    PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
    PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
    PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> 
    PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
    PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/> 
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
    PREFIX wds: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/statement/> 
    PREFIX wdv: <http://www.wikidata.org/value/> 
    PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
    PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
ASK WHERE {
  ?year wdt:P31 wd:Q577;  # ?year is an instance of a year
        wdt:P585 ?date.  # ?date is the point in time for ?year
  FILTER(?date > "1999-01-00T00:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime)  # Only consider years after 1999
  ?record wdt:P1001 wd:Q794;  # ?record is about Iran
           wdt:P2250 ?le.  # ?le is the life expectancy
  ?nextYear wdt:P31 wd:Q577;
            wdt:P585 ?nextDate;
            wdt:P1001 wd:Q794;
            wdt:P2250 ?nextLe.
  FILTER(?nextDate = (?date + "P1Y"^^xsd:duration))  # ?nextYear is the year immediately following ?year
  FILTER(?nextLe > ?le)  # life expectancy must increase
}

question.string: What are the German names of academic disciplines containing “linguistik”?

query.sparql:
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>
    PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
    PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
    PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
    PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> 
    PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
    PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/> 
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
    PREFIX wds: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/statement/> 
    PREFIX wdv: <http://www.wikidata.org/value/> 
    PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
    PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?germanName WHERE {
  ?subject wdt:P31 wd:Q11862829;   # instance of academic discipline
          rdfs:label ?label.
  FILTER(CONTAINS(LCASE(?label), "linguistik") && LANG(?label) = "de").
  ?subject rdfs:label ?germanName.
  FILTER(LANG(?germanName) = "de")
}

question.string: What event killed the most people in the years 1910 to 1920?

query.sparql:
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>
    PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
    PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
    PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
    PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> 
    PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
    PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/> 
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
    PREFIX wds: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/statement/> 
    PREFIX wdv: <http://www.wikidata.org/value/> 
    PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
    PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?event WHERE {
  ?event wdt:P31 wd:Q1656682;   # Instance of disaster
         wdt:P580 ?start_date;  # Start time
         wdt:P582 ?end_date;    # End time
         wdt:P1120 ?deaths.     # Number of deaths
  FILTER(YEAR(?start_date) >= 1910 && YEAR(?end_date) <= 1920)
}
ORDER BY DESC(?deaths)
LIMIT 1

question.string: Who is the soccer player with the most goals in their career?

query.sparql:
PREFIX wikibase: <http://wikiba.se/ontology#>
    PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
    PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
    PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
    PREFIX bd: <http://www.bigdata.com/rdf#>
    PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> 
    PREFIX geo: <http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#>
    PREFIX psn: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/value-normalized/> 
    PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> 
    PREFIX wds: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/statement/> 
    PREFIX wdv: <http://www.wikidata.org/value/> 
    PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>
    PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/> PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?player ?playerLabel (MAX(?goals) AS ?maxGoals)
WHERE 
{
  ?player wdt:P106 wd:Q937857;  # instance of a football player
          p:P54 ?teamstatement.
  ?teamstatement ps:P54 ?team; 
                 pq:P1351 ?goals.
  SERVICE wikibase:label { bd:serviceParam wikibase:language "en". }
}
GROUP BY ?player ?playerLabel
ORDER BY DESC(?maxGoals)
LIMIT 1

  }
}
